parts.part: Mr Walpole Dr Warton Mrs Carter Lady Herries Dr

relation.text: came home wth . Mr V . at 11 oClock Monday
1784 dreſsd in a Habit it was so cold for all day at ½ past 12 had ye Dſs . of Portland s
read from ¼ before 6 till past 10 oClock a Manuscript -- ye life of Epaminondas -- by a Mr. Oxendon who has been dead some years
sat ½ an hour with us -- a frost & snow as yesterday
read in my room till near 2 Mrs. Delany letters . 22 d . Janry 1784
Thursday The Dſs . Dr .. of Portland Coach at ½ past 12 -- went
went to bed at 12 oClock . Lady Dartrey call 'd when I was out in ye Morning 23 d . Janry . 1784
read an Eclogue of ye . Man : pastoral of Delia written some years
found notes & c letter from Miſs H More -- Miſs W King had call 'd upon me -- Tuesday
went to bed past 12 28 th . Janry 1784
Wednesday had my B . upstairs dreſs 'd
was released from her sufferings last Monday
Thursday -- dreſs 'd for ye . day A M went out
read after I was undreſs 'd till near 12 Sunday
had written to Miſs Boyle on one of her Birth days
read in ye . new whole Duty of Man . & c . Su Mo nday 2 d . Febry . 1784
came to me for a short time
told me to night she was 69 Years
got to my room till 1 -- in ye . Morning Wednesday
Thursday . dreſs 'd when I got up
did not expect him in London this Winter
had enquired after me yesterday Morning
1784 . Dreſs 'd for ye . day -- at 12 o'Clock ye . Prince of Wales came
went to my room 11 th . Febry . 1784
came in -- talk 'd of the Great Concert of Musick wch . is to be in honor of Mrs : W . of on ye . 21 st . April
talk 'd of Lord Stormont who is now
found a letter & c from my Dr . Friend Lord S——t Friday
gain 'd from her some information of the Dickenson family it was 3 years
din 'd at home wth . Mr. D : Jun
1784 Spent all ye . Morning alone . at 4 Mr. V . s
1784 -- at ten oClock Lord Exeter came
2 Years of age a little Man -- look
3 years . Dſs . of P . had not left
ten years with my friend & is very sincerely attach
wish 'd her too well not to be glad she was now
some time in Spain -- one day
